---
title: Spicy Salsa Verde Shrimp Tacos with Crema & Pico de Gallo
description: You know what time it is—it’s taco time! So, let’s get with the program: To start these spicy tacos, ground turkey is first seasoned with our smoky Mexican spice blend then sizzled with zesty green salsa for a flavorful filling. You’ll spoon it over steamy tortillas and top with quick homemade pico de gallo and cooling crema. A bright squeeze of fresh lemon juice completes this hearty handheld meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65baa730f6debb5c45b6bd2d-bd77d043.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65baa730f6debb5c45b6bd2d.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spicy-salsa-verde-shrimp-tacos-65baa730f6debb5c45b6bd2d
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Central America
